plot: Bruce gathers up all the kids in the family to join him on a camping trip to Nevada. However, when Khloe finds out how close the campsite is to Area 51, she arranges a slight detour to go alien hunting! Meanwhile, Kris' very own talk show is finally debuting--but she's extremely put off when she doesn't feel any love or support from the rest of her family. Will her tears knock some compassion into her kids' hearts? Plus, Lamar's erratic behavior becomes more apparent to the rest of the family when he starts phoning constantly while Khloe's away.—Anonymous
